      <title>香港监管警告后，Sprocomm 股价暴跌 91%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/sprocomm-crashes-91-within-minutes-after-regulator-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前监管机构就该公司股权结构过于紧密发出警告，导致名不见经传的手机和电子产品制造商 Sprocomm Intelligence Ltd. 的股价在香港暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/sprocomm-crashes-91-within-minutes-after-regulator-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 03:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
